  "title": "Best Pizza in Town",
  "difficulty": "Easy",
  "question_text": "<div class=\"paragraph\">Suppose a newspaper claims that <span class=\"tex2jax_process\">$50\\%$</span> of all residents in a town say that Restaurant <span class=\"tex2jax_process\">$A$</span> has the best pizza in the town. A local fact-checker decides that he wants to test this claim and takes a SRS of <span class=\"tex2jax_process\">$50$</span> residents from the town and asked them what Restaurant's pizza they prefer. In his sample, <span class=\"tex2jax_process\">$45\\%$</span> of people say they prefer Restaurant <span class=\"tex2jax_process\">$A$</span>. </div><div class=\"paragraph\">The fact-checker then decides to simulate the responses to see if <span class=\"tex2jax_process\">$45\\%$</span> is a possible outcome if the population proportion is known to be <span class=\"tex2jax_process\">$50\\%$</span>. Given is the fact-checker's sampling distribution for <span class=\"tex2jax_process\">$\\hat{p}$</span>, the sample proportion of local residents that prefer Restaurant <span class=\"tex2jax_process\">$A$</span>. </div><div class=\"u-overflow-x_hidden\"><div class=\"image-supplement__resizable\" style=\"position: relative; user-select: auto; width: 100%; height: 480px; max-height: 560px; min-width: 100%; min-height: 152px; box-sizing: border-box; flex-shrink: 0;\"><figure class=\"image-supplement__figure\" data-testid=\"image-supplement-default-display\"><div class=\"image-supplement__image-container\"><div class=\"image-supplement__controls\"><div style=\"display: inline-block;\"><button class=\"a-button a-button--m a-button-outlined--secondary a-button--secondary a-button--circle m-icon-button image-supplement__controls-button m-icon-button--size-s\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Hide Image\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" data-prefix=\"far\" data-icon=\"eye\" class=\"svg-inline--fa fa-eye a-icon content-inherit a-icon--size-inherit\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 576 512\"><path fill=