  "correct_answer": "<strong>Choice 'B'</strong> is the correct answer. ",
  "solution": "The above dot plot represents the simulation of local residents selecting their favorite restaurant's pizza with a known proportion of <span class=\"tex2jax_process\"><span class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"></span><span id=\"MathJax-Element-16974-Frame\" class=\"mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML\" tabindex=\"0\" data-mathml=\"<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>0.50</mn></math>\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"font-size: 114%; position: relative;\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-91188\" class=\"mjx-math\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-91189\" class=\"mjx-mrow\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-91190\" class=\"mjx-mn\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R\" style=\"padding-top: 0.387em; padding-bottom: 0.387em;\">0.50</span></span></span></span><span class=\"MJX_Assistive_MathML\" role=\"presentation\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>0.50</mn></math></span></span><script type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-16974\">0.50</script></span> who prefer Restaurant <span class=\"tex2jax_process\"><span class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"></span><span id=\"MathJax-Element-16975-Frame\" class=\"mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML\" tabindex=\"0\" data-mathml=\"<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>A</mi></math>\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"font-size: 114%; position: relative;\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-91191\" class=\"mjx-math\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-91192\" class=\"mjx-mrow\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-91193\" class=\"mjx-mi\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I\" style=\"padding-top: 0.496em; padding-bottom: 0.277em;\">A</span></span></span></span><span class=\"MJX_Assistive_MathML\" role=\"presentation\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>A</mi></math></span></span><script type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-16975\">A</script></span>. The fact-checker decided that he wanted to simulate the newspaper claim that stated that <span class=\"tex2jax_process\"><span class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"></span><span id=\"MathJax-Element-16976-Frame\" class=\"mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML\" tabindex=\"0\" data-mathml=\"<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>50</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0025;</mi></math>\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"font-size: 114%; position: relative;\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-91194\" class=\"mjx-math\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-91195\" class=\"mjx-mrow\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-91196\" class=\"mjx-mn\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R\" style=\"padding-top: 0.387em; padding-bottom: 0.387em;\">50</span></span><span id=\"MJXc-Node-91197\" class=\"mjx-mi\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R\" style=\"padding-top: 0.441em; padding-bottom: 0.387em;\">%</span></span></span></span><span class=\"MJX_Assistive_MathML\" role=\"presentation\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>50</mn><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">%</mi></math></span></span><script type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-16976\">50\\%</script></span> of the local town preferred Restaurant <span class=\"tex2jax_process\"><span class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"></span><span id=\"MathJax-Element-16977-Frame\" class=\"mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML\" tabindex=\"0\" data-mathml=\"<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>A</mi></math>\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"font-size: 114%; position: relative;\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-91198\" class=\"mjx-math\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-91199\" class=\"mjx-mrow\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-91200\" class=\"mjx-mi\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I\" style=\"padding-top: 0.496em; padding-bottom: 0.277em;\">A</span></span></span></span><span class=\"MJX_Assistive_MathML\" role=\"presentation\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>A</mi></math></span></span><script type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-16977\">A</script></span>. \n\nTherefore, each dot on the dot plot represents one trial of the simulation, which will provide us with the proportion of local residents that prefer Restaurant <span class=\"tex2jax_process\"><span class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"></span><span id=\"MathJax-Element-16978-Frame\" class=\"mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML\" tabindex=\"0\" data-mathml=\"<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>A</mi></math>\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"font-size: 114%; position: relative;\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-91201\" class=\"mjx-math\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-91202\" class=\"mjx-mrow\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-91203\" class=\"mjx-mi\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I\" style=\"padding-top: 0.496em; padding-bottom: 0.277em;\">A</span></span></span></span><span class=\"MJX_Assistive_MathML\" role=\"presentation\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>A</mi></math></span></span><script type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-16978\">A</script></span>'s pizza. \n\n<strong>Choice 'B\"</strong> is correct. ",
  "distractor_explanations": {
    "A": "<strong>Choice 'A'</strong> is incorrect. In order to be the number of people, the numbers on the dot plot would have to be whole numbers, as the number of people would be a discrete variable. ",
    "C": "<strong>Choice 'C'</strong> is incorrect. Each dot only represents a singular trial. <span class=\"tex2jax_process\"><span class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"></span><span id=\"MathJax-Element-16979-Frame\" class=\"mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML\" tabindex=\"0\" data-mathml=\"<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>50</mn></math>\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"font-size: 114%; position: relative;\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-91204\" class=\"mjx-math\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-91205\" class=\"mjx-mrow\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-91206\" class=\"mjx-mi\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I\" style=\"padding-top: 0.222em; padding-bottom: 0.277em;\">n</span></span><span id=\"MJXc-Node-91207\" class=\"mjx-mo MJXc-space3\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R\" style=\"padding-top: 0.058em; padding-bottom: 0.332em;\">=</span></span><span id=\"MJXc-Node-91208\" class=\"mjx-mn MJXc-space3\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R\" style=\"padding-top: 0.387em; padding-bottom: 0.387em;\">50</span></span></span></span><span class=\"MJX_Assistive_MathML\" role=\"presentation\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>50</mn></math></span></span><script type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-16979\">n=50</script></span> is talking about the number of people from each trial, not the number of trials. ",
    "D": "<strong>Choice 'D'</strong> is incorrect. The average number of people who stated their preferred Restaurant <span class=\"tex2jax_process\"><span class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"></span><span id=\"MathJax-Element-16980-Frame\" class=\"mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML\" tabindex=\"0\" data-mathml=\"<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>A</mi></math>\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"font-size: 114%; position: relative;\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-91209\" class=\"mjx-math\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-91210\" class=\"mjx-mrow\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-91211\" class=\"mjx-mi\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I\" style=\"padding-top: 0.496em; padding-bottom: 0.277em;\">A</span></span></span></span><span class=\"MJX_Assistive_MathML\" role=\"presentation\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>A</mi></math></span></span><script type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-16980\">A</script></span> would represent a sample mean, not a sample proportion. ",
    "E": "<strong>Choice 'E'</strong> is incorrect. Each dot only represents a singular trial, while also showing the proportion of people do in fact <em>did</em> prefer Restaurant <span class=\"tex2jax_process\"><span class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"></span><span id=\"MathJax-Element-16981-Frame\" class=\"mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML\" tabindex=\"0\" data-mathml=\"<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>A</mi></math>\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"font-size: 114%; position: relative;\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-91212\" class=\"mjx-math\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-91213\" class=\"mjx-mrow\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-91214\" class=\"mjx-mi\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I\" style=\"padding-top: 0.496em; padding-bottom: 0.277em;\">A</span></span></span></span><span class=\"MJX_Assistive_MathML\" role=\"presentation\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>A</mi></math></span></span><script type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-16981\">A</script></span>."
